# Naming Conventions
- Components: PascalCase
- File names: PascalCase
- Props: camelCase
- Custom hooks: use{Name}
- Context: {Name}Context

# Component Structure
- Use functional components
- Props type definitions required
- Separate style files
- Follow single responsibility principle

# Import Order
1. React related
2. Three.js related
3. React Three Fiber related
4. Components
5. Custom hooks
6. Utilities
7. Types
8. Styles

